 experimental research and theory can be applied in historical and institutional studies. This book will be a key resource in social science methodology courses at all levels.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 31. Jan 2022) 4aSociology -- Theory and Methods. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Methodology.2bisacsh1 aWalker, Henry A., eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978080476783540uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780804767835423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780804767835/original  aGBV-deGruyter-alles